tree <- read.tree("./Data/VP7/Global/VP7.aln5.fas.nwk")
tip_metadata <- read.table("./Data/VP7/Global/Annotation.txt", sep="\t", header=TRUE,check.names=FALSE, stringsAsFactor=F)


pp7 <- ggtree(tree) %<+% tip_metadata + geom_tippoint(aes(color=Period), size=1.5)+
  scale_color_manual(values=c("black", "red","blue"))
